    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voodoo Fishin’ is a 1–4 player online co-op creepy-cozy fishing game featuring proximity voice chat and swamp-dwelling surprises.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture into the bayou with friends in search of rare and legendary fish. The deeper you go, the stranger things get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish together. Laugh together. Try not to lose your haul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die, the swamp keeps your catch.<br>  <br><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/cc5b52be6e913bbe420b71ea83ae60b1.webp?t=1771868074\" width=605 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo provides access to the full core gameplay systems, but limits world exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/884d4a23d3c5a5f98df715a148816c18.webp?t=1771868074\" width=605 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/24546b559562c114e9012fb68c1681a5.poster.avif?t=1771868074\" width=608 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/24546b559562c114e9012fb68c1681a5.webm?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/24546b559562c114e9012fb68c1681a5.mp4?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your puppet angler and hit the dock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/25e38bd6fffaef0d011b7db99a473b8f.webp?t=1771868074\" width=605 height=55 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/bee77b2ea08914c91b28e6c1f314efe6.poster.avif?t=1771868074\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/bee77b2ea08914c91b28e6c1f314efe6.webm?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/bee77b2ea08914c91b28e6c1f314efe6.mp4?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It’s chill… until it isn’t. This swamp hunts back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/a7b0aa4260e7afb2a800605235b4738b.webp?t=1771868074\" width=605 height=55 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/ea9e1a4bc21eb99f897034c40576292b.poster.avif?t=1771868074\" width=608 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/ea9e1a4bc21eb99f897034c40576292b.webm?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/ea9e1a4bc21eb99f897034c40576292b.mp4?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you make it back alive, the Fish Monger pays by the pound.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/ad12781dea149e389aa6c5f78fe411f6.webp?t=1771868074\" width=605 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/072acd4c252bc09abc74ee28798b709a.poster.avif?t=1771868074\" width=608 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/072acd4c252bc09abc74ee28798b709a.webm?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071240/extras/072acd4c252bc09abc74ee28798b709a.mp4?t=1771868074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your Bait, Reels, and Rods to chase bigger and rarer fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play Forever</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The swamp doesn’t run on corporate servers. Voodoo Fishin’ is <i>self-hosted</i>, so once you’re in, you can always jump back in with friends. No server shutdowns. No “service discontinued.”<br><br>The swamp stays open as long as you can stay alive.</p>",
